summary:
Place the daedra text file in your Skyrim directory
Start the game
Open dev console
Enter bat daedra
PWN LIKE A DAEDRIC BOSS
descriptionHtml:
This is a text file that gives you the full daedric set of armor and weapons.
Daedric Mods like the crosbow and mask are not included.
author: NKLH4X0R
